ZOMG! ITS A MAP!!

Here's how it goes:

- 10 v 10
- CTs and Ts both spawn with 1 hp
- Spawn with a knife and a flashbang each
- YOU MUST KILL EACH OTHERRR

I made this cuz i was really bored... D: ! And to practice my clan's knifing and flashing skillz...especially flashnade killz! :3!

Not really that creative, but hey, this only took 'bout like 1 hour and a half :\ Not too long lol! Hope you guys like it!

- TeamRK // Firestar (aka Kenblah)
